## Answer (1)

You are using the wrong type for the `clilen` argument to `accept()`. It should be `socklen_t`, not `socklen_t*`.

```
newsockfd = accept(sockfd, (struct sockaddr *) &cli_addr, (socklen_t*) &clilen);
```

should be:

```
newsockfd = accept(sockfd, (struct sockaddr *) &cli_addr, &clilen);
```

Also, you are not checking the return value of `accept()` for errors. You should be doing this:

```
newsockfd = accept(sockfd, (struct sockaddr *) &cli_addr, &clilen);

